  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we went our business the same way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Really kind of-- that-- that-- from that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was not in '42.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was already-- because in '44, they took us away and that was kind of like-- not '40-- that winter, but I don't know if it was the end of-- that's '43, let's put it that way.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I made the mistake, the '42.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was at the end of '43 or the beginning of '44 because then when it was already kind of before-- close to the-- the-- before they took us a way.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Taken away.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, as I say, that-- when it came already before Pesach, we were kind of-- as I say, we knew from-- from the sheriff that they're talking about that they're gonna take away the Jews.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there is something else what we know, especially our family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, I am jumping from one to another.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had two sisters living in Holland, and we got-- they were home before the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It '35 or in '37 when they start already brewing the war in Germany and [? thing. ?] They came home for a vacation, and they didn't finish it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- you know, they heard that thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They got a letter because just the sister came home, and my brother-in-law didn't.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they left, they went back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so after a while, we stop getting letters from them, from Holland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we stopped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew, well, it's a war and things.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
